    dc:creator "Clark, Vincent Ralph; Bentley, Joanne; Dold, Anthony P.; Zikishe, Vathiswa; Barker, Nigel P." ;
    dc:date "2016" ;
    dc:title "The rediscovery of the Great Winterberg endemic Lotononis harveyi B. - E. van Wyk after 147 years, and notes on the poorly known Amathole endemic Macowania revoluta Oliv. (southern Great Escarpment, South Africa)" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/phytokeys.62.8348.figure1>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/phytokeys.62.8348.plate1> ;
